review:
Omellete + Fried Egg + Coconut Water, works everytime, even the last boss kneels before the mighty power of EGG !!!

That aside, this is more like "remake polished version" of Suikoden 2; Its hard to describe it but for veteran players you must be know it feels, it vibes, it gimmicks; Im not sayinig this is bad, i even hooked up on this for several hours; 

The UI for comparing stats when purchasing armors could be better though, for example a List of hero names and on the right side, the status numbers (increase/decrease) 

For money making, trading is ridiculous and only serve for recruiting only, you can make tons of money when reaching certain builds on your castle; 

The one i hate most is dune racing, my (crappy, for work purpose) laptop cannot handle the FPS and i must downgrade every setting and close any program; Ugh... 

That being said, try this one...
